Rock, Paper, Scissors - Another version of this coding puzzle written in Drupal.
Object Oriented, Fully PHPUnit PHP Tested, Jasmine Tested OO MVC JS and Cucumber BDD Tested

The build is ready to pass the following

1) functional tests - cucumber
2) php md tests - phpmd
3) phpunit tests - phpunit

All available in their respective build/config folders, just run execute-*.php

